origin: Gateway start blocked: set gateway.mode=local (current: ${mode ?? "unset"}) or pass --allow-unconfigured.
translate: 网关启动受阻: 设置 gateway.mode=local (当前: ${mode ?? "unset"}) 或传递 --allow-unconfigured。

origin: "gateway.remote.token" is for remote CLI calls; it does not enable local gateway auth.
translate: "gateway.remote.token" 用于远程 CLI 调用；它不启用本地网关认证。

origin: Gateway auth is set to token but no token is configured.
translate: 网关认证设置为令牌，但未配置令牌。

origin: Gateway auth is set to password but no password is configured.
translate: 网关认证设置为密码，但未配置密码。
设置 gateway.auth.password (或 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PASSWORD)，或传递 --password。

origin: Refusing to bind gateway to ${bind} without authentication.
translate: 拒绝在无认证的情况下将网关绑定到 ${bind}。
设置 gateway.auth.token/password (或 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN/OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PASSWORD) 或传递 --token/--password。

origin: Gateway failed to start: ${errMessage}\nIf the gateway is supervised, stop it with: ${formatCliCommand("openclaw gateway stop")}
translate: 网关启动失败: ${errMessage}\n如果网关受监管，请使用以下命令停止: ${formatCliCommand("openclaw gateway stop")}

origin: Bind mode ("loopback"|"lan"|"tailnet"|"auto"|"custom"). Default: config gateway.bind (or loopback).
translate: 绑定模式 ("loopback"|"lan"|"tailnet"|"auto"|"custom")。默认为配置 gateway.bind (或 loopback)。
